Text: a group of backpackers travelling thru Brazil in search of cheap booze, drugs & sex discover that their body parts are worth a considerable amount of money on the brazilian black market. Don't ya just love it when stupid gringo muthafuckers with too much money get chopped up for their body parts, after all, there's no National Health Service in Brazil.
